'263\t1\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Agents of Baa") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Have you noticed how Temples of Baa have been sprouting up throughout the kingdom?  They're everywhere, and I for one think it's an ominous development.  Although they offer free healing, they don't seem to be doing it out of kindness– there must be a method to their madness!") + '\r\n'
