'279\t1\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Dwarves") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "If the old tales are true, the dwarves were once just like the rest of us, but before the Crossing, the dwarves lived in a place where they and everything around them weighed a lot more.  The stories say this made them very short and very strong, and they haven't changed since.") + '\r\n'
